{"id":"b332ef34-ef1b-451e-bec9-9e0f4b9b2109","name":"Reborn Evil [NIKKE]","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>\"<mark style=\"background-color: rgb(161, 20, 23); color: inherit;\">A D-Wave has been detected in a large mansion on the Outer Rim.</mark></em></span><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(161, 20, 23); color: inherit;\"><br></mark></em><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(161, 20, 23); color: inherit;\">At the same time, clues surrounding mysterious disappearances in the Ark also point to the same, strange mansion...</mark></em></span><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(161, 20, 23); color: inherit;\"><br></mark></em><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(161, 20, 23); color: inherit;\">Upon learning that everything is linked to a cult named \"Torch of Salvation,\" the Commander decides to head for the Outer Rim with the Perilous Siege squad</mark>.\"</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(196, 196, 196); color: inherit;\">A string of disappearances leads the Commander, alongside </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(196, 196, 196); color: inherit;\">D</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(196, 196, 196); color: inherit;\"> and </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(196, 196, 196); color: inherit;\">K</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(196, 196, 196); color: inherit;\"> of Perilous Siege, to a cult called the </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(196, 196, 196); color: inherit;\">Torch of Salvation</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(196, 196, 196); color: inherit;\">, whose leader </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(196, 196, 196); color: inherit;\">Elseria Nine</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(196, 196, 196); color: inherit;\">—a grief-stricken therapist—created the </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(196, 196, 196); color: inherit;\">NEO-Virus</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(196, 196, 196); color: inherit;\"> from off-world Umbrella data to “purify” humanity.<br>During the investigation, they join forces with </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(196, 196, 196); color: inherit;\">Ada Wong</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(196, 196, 196); color: inherit;\">, </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(196, 196, 196); color: inherit;\">Jill Valentine</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(196, 196, 196); color: inherit;\">, </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(196, 196, 196); color: inherit;\">Claire Redfield</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(196, 196, 196); color: inherit;\">, and </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(196, 196, 196); color: inherit;\">A.C.P.U.’s</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(196, 196, 196); color: inherit;\"> </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(196, 196, 196); color: inherit;\">Quiry</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(196, 196, 196); color: inherit;\"> and </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(196, 196, 196); color: inherit;\">Poli</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(196, 196, 196); color: inherit;\">, uncovering a hidden lab beneath the Outer Rim mansion where the cult used the missing citizens as test subjects for </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(196, 196, 196); color: inherit;\">Project: Reborn Evil</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(196, 196, 196); color: inherit;\">.</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">YONICHIWA AND HAPPY HUZZOWEEN!!</p><ul><li><p>I'ts been a been a bit, this ones pretty juicy, so thank goodness for lore books</p></li><li><p>also D and K are wearing this, cause i thought it'd be fu","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"Ucq2k7x6ong0okiTIDTrK.webp","creator":"ZannyEX","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","📺 Anime","🤖 Robot","👭 Multiple","🛸 Sci-Fi"],"chats":135,"messages":532,"created_at":"2025-10-30T19:40:14.164886+00:00"}